<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1840,2010]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,310,1840,1866]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Observations</emphasis>
. This genus is widely distributed in the basins of 
<collectingCountry box="[883,941,1840,1866]" name="India" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">India</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Khosla, A. &amp; Sahni, A." box="[957,1210,1840,1866]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="57 - 78" refId="ref14514" refString="Khosla, A. &amp; Sahni, A. (2000) Late Cretaceous (Maastrichtian) ostracodes from the Lameta Formation, Jabalpur Cantonment area, Madhya Pradesh, India. Journal of the Palaeontological Society of India, 45, 57 - 78." type="journal article" year="2000">Khosla &amp; Sahni 2000</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Whatley, R. &amp; Bajpai, S." pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="385 - 409" refId="ref17471" refString="Whatley, R. &amp; Bajpai, S. (2000 a) A new fauna of Late Cretaceous non-marine Ostracoda from the Deccan intertrappean beds of Lakshmipur, Kachchh (Kutch) District, Gujarat, Western India. Revista Espanola de Micropaleontologia, 32, 385 - 409." type="journal article" year="2000">Whatley &amp; Bajpai, 2000a</bibRefCitation>
, b and c; 
<bibRefCitation author="Bajpai, S. &amp; Whatley, R. C." box="[328,597,1876,1902]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="91 - 111" refId="ref12967" refString="Bajpai, S. &amp; Whatley, R. C. (2001) Late Cretaceous non- marine ostracods from the Deccan Intertrappean beds, Kora (Western Kachchh, India). Revista EspanTola de Micropalaeontologiia, 33, 91 - 111." type="journal article" year="2001">Bajpai &amp; Whatley 2001</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Whatley, R. &amp; Bajpai, S. &amp; Whittaker, J. E." box="[608,843,1876,1902]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="75 - 86" refId="ref17778" refString="Whatley, R., Bajpai, S. &amp; Whittaker, J. E. (2003 a) Freshwater Ostracoda from the Upper Cretaceous intertrappean beds at Mamoni (Kota District), southeastern Rajasthan, India. Revista Espanola de Micropaleontologia, 35 (1), 75 - 86." type="journal article" year="2003">
Whatley 
<emphasis box="[710,766,1876,1902]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">et al.</emphasis>
2003a
</bibRefCitation>
, b and c; 
<bibRefCitation author="Khosla, S. C. &amp; Nagori, M. L." box="[949,1208,1876,1903]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="573 - 580" refId="ref14560" refString="Khosla, S. C. &amp; Nagori, M. L. (2005) A restudy of ostracode fauna from the Inter-trappean beds of Anjar, Kachchh District, Gujarat. Journal of the Geological Society of India, 66 (5), 573 - 580." type="journal article" year="2005">Khosla &amp; Nagori 2005</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Khosla, S. C. &amp; Nagori, M. L. &amp; Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S." box="[1219,1436,1876,1902]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="724 - 732" refId="ref14610" refString="Khosla, S. C., Nagori, M. L., Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S. (2009 a) Mixed marine, brackish water and non-marine microfaunal association in the Inter-trappean beds (Early Palaeocene) of Jhilmili, Chhindwara District, Madhya Pradesh. Journal of the Geological Society of India, 73 (5), 724 - 732. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / s 12594 - 009 - 0056 - 2" type="journal article" year="2009">
Khosla 
<emphasis box="[1305,1361,1876,1902]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">et al.</emphasis>
2009a
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Khosla, S. C. &amp; Nagori, M. L. &amp; Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S." box="[197,403,1912,1938]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="223 - 245" refId="ref14701" refString="Khosla, S. C., Nagori, M. L., Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S. (2011) Early Danian lacustrine - brackish water Ostracoda from the Deccan Intertrappean beds near Jhilmili, Chhindwara District, Madhya Pradesh, India. Micropaleontology, 57 (3), 223 - 245. https: // doi. org / 10.47894 / mpal. 57.3.02" type="journal article" year="2011">
Khosla 
<emphasis box="[282,337,1912,1938]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">et al.</emphasis>
2011
</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation author="Khosla, S. C. &amp; Nagori, M. L. &amp; Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S." box="[420,653,1912,1938]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="724 - 732" refId="ref14610" refString="Khosla, S. C., Nagori, M. L., Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S. (2009 a) Mixed marine, brackish water and non-marine microfaunal association in the Inter-trappean beds (Early Palaeocene) of Jhilmili, Chhindwara District, Madhya Pradesh. Journal of the Geological Society of India, 73 (5), 724 - 732. https: // doi. org / 10.1007 / s 12594 - 009 - 0056 - 2" type="journal article" year="2009">
Khosla 
<emphasis box="[505,560,1912,1938]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">et al.</emphasis>
(2009a)
</bibRefCitation>
transferred this genus to 
<taxonomicName authority="Sars, (1889)" authorityName="Sars" authorityYear="1889" box="[930,1205,1912,1938]" class="Ostracoda" family="Cyprididae" genus="Stenocypris" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF,CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[930,1061,1912,1938]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Stenocypris</emphasis>
Sars, (1889)
</taxonomicName>
. In the present study, the species found was treated as belonging to the genus 
<taxonomicName box="[781,946,1948,1974]" class="Ostracoda" family="Cyprididae" genus="Mongolianella" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Podocopida" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[781,946,1948,1974]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">Mongolianella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but we emphasize the need for a comparative study with the forms described by 
<bibRefCitation author="Khosla, S. C. &amp; Nagori, M. L. &amp; Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S." box="[587,813,1984,2010]" pageId="5" pageNumber="540" pagination="223 - 245" refId="ref14701" refString="Khosla, S. C., Nagori, M. L., Jakhar, S. R. &amp; Rathore, A. S. (2011) Early Danian lacustrine - brackish water Ostracoda from the Deccan Intertrappean beds near Jhilmili, Chhindwara District, Madhya Pradesh, India. Micropaleontology, 57 (3), 223 - 245. https: // doi. org / 10.47894 / mpal. 57.3.02" type="journal article" year="2011">
Khosla 
<emphasis box="[674,730,1984,2010]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="540">et al.</emphasis>
(2011)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
